{
  "stem": "1173.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She used to go to Marienbad and Carlsbad for cures.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father, thank God, survived, and just passed away last July.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was 95 years old when he passed away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But also, after the war, we spent some time together in Lubeck, where I came after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, they moved to Israel, with his second wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He remarried in 1948.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so, since after the war, we spent just couple of months here on a visit, couple of months in Israel, or, later on, in Australia where they moved.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left Warsaw, I was-- that was '39-- about 14, 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left Warsaw November 15, 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father decided that I should leave Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was afraid that the, the German might, might kidnap me, because he had two jewelry stores.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and he sent me away with my cousins, two cousins, to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to, of course, go through the border between Russia and Germany, which was not far away from Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went by horse and buggy, and we had very few things with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only-- I remember, my father was in the jewelry business, so he gave me a box of his watches, which later on, I was selling in Bialystok, to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this way, I can support myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was in Bialystok a few months when the Russian decided that they, they declared that whoever wants to go back to Warsaw is free to do so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- of course, we had to sign papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They've allowed Jews who escaped Warsaw or, or the Germans to go back, if they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
